umber\">#fff</span>;<br>&#125;<br><span class=\"hljs-selector-class\">.active</span>&#123;<br>  <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">color</span>: <span class=\"hljs-number\">#f00</span>;<br>&#125;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>编写 JS 页面逻辑代码：</p>\n<p>index.js:</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight javascript\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><code class=\"hljs javascript\"><span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Page</span>(&#123;<br>  <span class=\"hljs-attr\">data</span>: &#123;<br>    <span class=\"hljs-attr\">items</span>: [<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;要闻&quot;</span>, <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;推荐&quot;</span>, <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;原创&quot;</span>, <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;热点&quot;</span>],<br>    <span class=\"hljs-attr\">curIdx</span>: <span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span><br>  &#125;,<br>  <span class=\"hljs-attr\">onItemTap</span>: <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\">event</span>)&#123;<br>    <span class=\"hljs-variable language_\">this</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title function_\">setData</span>(&#123;<span class=\"hljs-attr\">curIdx</span>: event.<span class=\"hljs-property\">mark</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">idx</span>&#125;);<br>  &#125;<br>&#125;)<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure>","prev":{"title":"微信小程序-view组件","link":"2023/04/22/Web/微信小程序/component/常用组件/32-微信小程序-view组件"},"next":{"title":"微信小程序-touches和changedTouches","link":"2023/04/20/Web/微信小程序/event/30-微信小程序-touches和changedTouches"},"plink":"http://example.com/2023/04/21/Web/微信小程序/example/31-微信小程序-案例练习/","toc":[{"id":"所需技术点","title":"所需技术点","index":"1"},{"id":"案例最终实现效果","title":"案例最终实